* {{tbox|pic=Serving platter detail.png|The serving platter is empty.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Searching food crates in the kitchen===
* '''Player:''' I should wait until I've gotten a food order before I start taking things.
* {{tact|end}}

==Serving the customers==
''This dialogue is the same when serving all three NPCs. For ease they will be referred to as [Customer].''
===Talking to the customer===
* '''Player:''' Hello and welcome to the Blue Moon Inn!
* '''[Customer]:''' Hello! Merry Christmas!
* '''Player:''' Let me show you to your table.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the customer before picking a table===
* '''[Customer]:''' Can you show me to my table please?
* '''Player:''' Certainly, right this way!
* {{tact|end}}

===Serving a table when no customer is waiting===
* '''Player:''' I don't need to serve this table right now.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the customer after picking a table===
* '''Player:''' Hello and welcome to the Blue Moon Inn. Can I get you something to drink?
* '''[Customer]:''' Yes please! Can I have some [beverage]?
* '''Player:''' Certainly! Coming right up!
* {{tbox|pic=Beer glass detail.png|You can find various drinks at the bar.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Getting a drink from the bar===
* {{tbox|pic=Serving platter detail.png|You grab some [beverage] from the bar and put it on your serving platter.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Serving the table after getting the drink===
* '''Player:''' Here is your drink. Enjoy!
* '''[Customer]:''' Cheers!
* '''Player:''' Are you ready to order your Christmas dinner?
* '''[Customer]:''' Why, yes I am!
* '''[Customer]:''' For my main, I would like [main], and for my sides I would like [side 1], [side 2] and [side 3].
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the customer again before getting the order===
* '''Player:''' Are you ready to order your Christmas dinner?
* {{tact|above}}

===Serving the table after getting the order===
* '''Player:''' I should go get all the ingredients for their Christmas dinner.
* '''Player:''' I believe they wanted [main], with [side 1], [side 2] and [side 3].
* '''Player:''' I should ask the Cook where to find them.
* {{tact|end}}

===Searching the basement crates for the ingredients===
* {{tbox|pic=Serving platter detail.png|You place the [ingredient name] on your serving platter.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Serving the table with cooked food===
* '''Player:''' Here is your meal. Enjoy!
* '''[Customer]:''' Thank you!
* {{tact|If the player has more customers to serve.}}
** '''Player:''' I should go seat another guest!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tact|If the player has served all 3 customers.}}
** '''Player:''' Right, I think that's my job done! Time to grab a seat and have my own Christmas dinner!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the cook after greeting a customer===
* '''Player:''' Sorry to bother you, but what was I meant to be doing again?
* '''Cook:''' Have you greeted the guest yet?
* '''Player:''' Yeah!
* '''Cook:''' Well show them to an empty table then.
* '''Player:''' Oh, yeah, right, thanks boss!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the cook after seating a customer===
* '''Player:''' Sorry to bother you, but what was I meant to be doing again?
* '''Cook:''' Well, have you offered to take a drink order yet?
* '''Player:''' No...
* '''Cook:''' You should probably do that then. Go ask what drink our first{{Note|The cook always says first even if they are not the first guest to be seated}} guest would like.
* '''Player:''' Can do!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the cook after taking a drink order===
* '''Player:''' Sorry to bother you, but what was I meant to be doing again?
* '''Cook:''' Have you offered our guest a drink yet?
* '''Player:''' Yes! They wanted some [beverage].
* '''Cook:''' Well, all the drinks are behind the bar, not back here in the kitchen.
* '''Player:''' That would make sense. Thanks boss!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the cook before taking a food order===
* '''Player:''' Sorry to bother you, but what was I meant to be doing again?
* '''Cook:''' Have you taken their food order yet?
* '''Player:''' I dont{{sic}} think so... No. No I haven't.
* '''Cook:''' Well go and do that then!
* '''Player:''' Yes boss!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the cook after taking a food order===
* '''Player:''' I have a food order!
* '''Cook:''' Great! Just go grab all the ingredients from the basement and I'll cook it right up!
* '''Player:''' Isn't there any kitchen staff to do that?
* '''Cook:''' If I could afford kitchen staff, I wouldn't be paying you with a free meal, would I?
* '''Player:''' Good point. I'll go get those ingredients now.
* '''Player:''' I believe they ordered...
* '''Player:''' [main course], with [sides].
* {{tact|end}}

