==Completing the event==
===Talking to the cook===
* '''Cook:''' Good job, kid. That's your shift done!
* '''Player:''' Phew! Does that mean it's time for my Christmas dinner?
* '''Cook:''' Absolutely, you've earnt it!
* '''Cook:''' Go take a seat and I'll prepare you a meal you'll never forget!
* '''Player:''' Yippee!
* {{tact|end}}

===Sitting at the table===
* {{tcond|If the player has 10 or less empty spaces in their inventory:}}
** {{tbox|You need {{Colour|#ff0000|2-12}} more free inventory slots to receive your Christmas event rewards.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has 11 empty spaces in their inventory:}}
** {{tbox|You need {{Colour|#ff0000|1}} more free inventory slot to receive your Christmas event rewards.}}
* {{tcond|If the player has enough inventory space:}}
** {{tact|A cutscene plays where the cook brings the player Christmas dinner to their table. [[Mod_Freddie (2025 Christmas event)|Mod_Freddie]] can be seen outside the [[Puffin (2025 Christmas event)|puffin's]] pillory cell in the background, doing the [[cry]] emote.}}
** '''Cook:''' {{overhead|And for all your hard work...}}
** '''Cook:''' {{overhead|Here's your very own Christmas dinner!}}
** '''Player:''' {{overhead|Yippee!}}
** {{tact|The player does the [[Jump for Joy]] emote while the cook [[laugh]]s.}}
** {{tact|end}}

