==Misc. NPC Dialogue==
===Talking to [[Herquin]]===
* '''Player:''' Hello, Herquin. Merry Christmas!
* '''Herquin:''' Merry Christmas, [player name]!
* '''Herquin:''' It's hardly the Rising Sun Inn, but I guess it will do.
* '''Player:''' Oh? How come you're here instead then?
* '''Herquin:''' I'm not allowed back after... the incident.
* '''Player:''' The incident?
* '''Herquin:''' The Incident!
* '''Player:''' What happened?
* '''Herquin:''' It's too embarrassing, but let's just say I ruined a perfectly good table.
* '''Player:''' Right then...
* '''Player:''' Merry Christmas?
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to [[Doris]]===
